text: Luciana Reali (born 4 March 1936) is an Italian gymnast. She competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
